msgstr "<span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">🎓 ການຂາຍ</span>"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong/>To start an order in your Point of\n"
"                Sale (POS) session, scan or select all items. For products sold by weight (grams or\n"
"                kilograms), a window will pop up automatically. Enter the specific weight, and the\n"
"                final price will be calculated immediately.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong/>ເພື່ອເລີ່ມການສັ່ງຊື້ໃນຮອບການຂາຍ (POS) ຂອງທ່ານ, ໃຫ້ສະແກນ ຫຼື ເລືອກລາຍການສິນຄ້າ. ສຳລັບ"
"ສິນຄ້າທີ່ຂາຍຕາມນ້ຳໜັກ (ກຣາມ ຫຼື ກິໂລ), ປ່ອງຢ້ຽມຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ. ປ້ອນນ້ຳໜັກທີ່ລະບຸ, ແລະ ລາຄ"
"າສຸດທ້າຍຈະຖືກຄິດໄລ່ທັນທີ.<br/>"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>\n"
"                <u>Process</u>\n"
"            </strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>\n"
"                <u>ຂະບວນການ</u>\n"
"            </strong>"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "<u>1. Configure Products and Their Display</u>"
msgstr "<u>1. ຕັ້ງຄ່າສິນຄ້າ ແລະ ການສະແດງຜົນ</u>"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "<u>1. Create and Categorize Products</u>"
msgstr "<u>1. ສ້າງ ແລະ ແຍກໝວດໝູ່ສິນຄ້າ</u>"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "<u>2. Define Replenishment Methods</u>"
msgstr "<u>2. ກຳນົດວິທີການເຕີມສິນຄ້າ</u>"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "<u>2. Review General E-commerce Policies</u>"
msgstr "<u>2. ກວດສອບນະໂຍບາຍອີຄອມເມີຊທົ່ວໄປ</u>"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "<u>3. Set Up Payment and Delivery</u>"
msgstr "<u>3. ຕັ້ງຄ່າການຊຳລະເງິນ ແລະ ການຈັດສົ່ງ</u>"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "Accept multiple payment options: cash, card, and mobile payments."
msgstr "ຮອງຮັບຫຼາຍຕົວເລືອກການຊຳລະເງິນ: ເງິນສົດ, ບັດ ແລະ ການຊຳລະຜ່ານມືຖື."

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.pricing
msgid "Account &amp; Sales management"
msgstr "ການຈັດການບັນຊີ &amp; ການຂາຍ"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "Accurately <b>update the inventoried quantity</b>."
msgstr "<b>ອັບເດດຈຳນວນສິນຄ້າໃນສາງ</b> ຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Activating this feature allows the app to propose a replenishment quantity calculated\n"
"            over a set number of days. You can also apply a percentage factor if you anticipate a\n"
"            change in demand."
msgstr ""
"ການເປີດໃຊ້ຄຸນສົມບັດນີ້ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ App ສາມາດແນະນຳຈຳນວນການເຕີມສິນຄ້າທີ່ຄິດໄລ່\n"
"            ຕາມຈຳນວນມື້ທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດນຳໃຊ້ປັດໄຈເປີເຊັນໄດ້ ຫາກທ່ານຄາດການວ່າ\n"
"            ຈະມີການປ່ຽນແປງຂອງຄວາມຕ້ອງການ."

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.homepage
msgid "Agriculture Made Simple"
msgstr "ກະສິກຳທີ່ເຮັດໄດ້ງ່າຍ"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.homepage
msgid ""
"Agriculture produces essential food and goods through farming. It uses "
"technology and sustainable practices to boost productivity and address "
"climate challenges, playing a key role in food security, rural development, "
"and global trade."
msgstr ""
"ກະສິກຳຜະລິດອາຫານ ແລະ ສິນຄ້າທີ່ຈຳເປັນຜ່ານການເຮັດໄຮ່ເຮັດນາ. ມັນນຳໃຊ້ເຕັກໂນໂລຊີ ແລະ ແນວທາງທີ່ຍືນຍົງ"
"ເພື່ອເພີ່ມຜົນຜະລິດ ແລະ ຮັບມືກັບສິ່ງທ້າທາຍດ້ານສະພາບອາກາດ, ເຊິ່ງມີບົດບາດສຳຄັນໃນຄວາມໝັ້ນຄົງທາງດ້ານອາຫາ"
"ນ, ການພັດທະນາຊົນນະບົດ ແລະ ການຄ້າລະດັບໂລກ."

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model:product.attribute.value,name:agriculture_shop.product_attribute_value_11
msgid "AlwaysFirst"
msgstr "AlwaysFirst"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.red_revolution_tomato_seeds
msgid ""
"As the tomatoes ripen and mature, they are harvested at their peak, with a "
"focus on selecting the healthiest and most vigorous fruits. These fruits are"
" carefully processed to extract their seeds, which are then thoroughly "
"cleaned and fermented. Fermentation helps remove the gel-like coating around"
" the seeds, which can inhibit germination."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອໝາກເລັ່ນສຸກເຕັມທີ່, ພວກມັນຈະຖືກເກັບກ່ຽວໃນໄລຍະທີ່ດີທີ່ສຸດ, ໂດຍເນັ້ນໃສ່ການເລືອກໝາກທີ່ສົມບູນ ແລະ ແຂງແ"
"ຮງທີ່ສຸດ. ໝາກເລັ່ນເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຈະຖືກນຳໄປສະກັດເອົາແກ່ນຢ່າງລະມັດລະວັງ, ຈາກນັ້ນກໍທຳຄວາມສະອາດ ແລະ ບົ່ມ. ການ"
"ບົ່ມຈະຊ່ວຍກຳຈັດເມືອກທີ່ຫຸ້ມແກ່ນອອກ, ເຊິ່ງອາດຂັດຂວາງການງອກ."

