msgstr ""
"ໂດຍການອັບໂຫຼດຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງຂອງໂມດູນນີ້, ຖານຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຖືກ\n"
"            ເພີ່ມຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່ຈຳນວນໜຶ່ງແລ້ວ."

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model:product.template,name:agriculture_shop.product_product_6_product_template
msgid "Cauliflower Seeds"
msgstr "ແກ່ນພັນກະລໍ່າດອກ"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model:product.template,description_sale:agriculture_shop.product_product_6_product_template
msgid ""
"Cauliflower seeds are the starting point for growing nutritious and "
"versatile cauliflower plants. These small, potent seeds hold the potential "
"to yield a range of cauliflower varieties, offering a rewarding journey from"
" planting to harvesting in home gardens and farms alike."
msgstr ""
"ແກ່ນພັນກະລໍ່າດອກແມ່ນຈຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນສຳລັບການປູກກະລໍ່າດອກທີ່ມີຄຸນຄ່າທາງອາຫານສູງ. ແກ່ນພັນຂະໜາດນ້ອຍເຫຼົ່ານີ້ມີທ່າແ"
"ຮງທີ່ຈະໃຫ້ຜົນຜະລິດທີ່ຫຼາກຫຼາຍ, ເຮັດໃຫ້ການປູກຈົນເຖິງການເກັບກ່ຽວເປັນປະສົບການທີ່ດີທັງໃນສວນຄົວ ແລະ ໃນໄຮ່ນ"
"າ."

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.pricing
msgid "Complete CRM for any size team"
msgstr "CRM ຄົບວົງຈອນສຳລັບທີມງານທຸກຂະໜາດ"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.contactus
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.pricing
msgid "Contact us"
msgstr "ຕິດຕໍ່ພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.contactus
msgid ""
"Contact us about anything related to our company or services.<br/>We'll do "
"our best to get back to you as soon as possible."
msgstr ""
"ຕິດຕໍ່ພວກເຮົາກ່ຽວກັບທຸກສິ່ງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບບໍລິສັດ ຫຼື ການບໍລິການຂອງພວກເຮົາ.<br/>ພວກເຮົາຈະພະຍາຍາມຢ່າງສຸດ"
"ຄວາມສາມາດເພື່ອຕອບກັບທ່ານໃຫ້ໄວທີ່ສຸດ."

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model:product.template,name:agriculture_shop.product_product_9_product_template
msgid "Cucumber Seeds"
msgstr "ແກ່ນພັນໝາກແຕງ"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model:product.template,description_sale:agriculture_shop.product_product_9_product_template
msgid ""
"Cucumber seeds are the first step to cultivating refreshing and crunchy "
"cucumbers. These tiny seeds harbor the promise of abundant vines and a "
"bountiful harvest, allowing both gardeners and farmers to enjoy the "
"satisfaction of growing this hydrating and versatile vegetable."
msgstr ""
"ແກ່ນພັນໝາກແຕງແມ່ນບາດກ້າວທຳອິດໃນການປູກໝາກແຕງທີ່ສົດຊື່ນ ແລະ ກອບ. ແກ່ນນ້ອຍໆເຫຼົ່ານີ້ເປັນຈຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງເ"
"ຄືອທີ່ແຂງແຮງ ແລະ ຜົນຜະລິດທີ່ຫຼວງຫຼາຍ, ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຊາວສວນ ແລະ ຊາວກະສິກອນມີຄວາມສຸກໃນການປູກຜັກທີ່ຊ່ວຍເພີ່ມ"
